        <item>
            <title>TGS 2023《人中之龙》摊位美女如云   Kson、佐山爱现场面对观众 + 辣妹配钢管舞</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/22/tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/22/tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Long]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 09:46:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娱乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《人中之龙 7 国际版》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SEGA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TGS 2023]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人中之龙]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1194821</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>TGS 东京电玩展 2023 贵为每年日本电玩盛事，往往都水泄不通。而 SEGA 官方摊位大有绰头，非常识玩咁为观众准备钢管舞表演以及大量美艳《人中之龙》夜总会小姐。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194842" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>TGS 2023 SEGA 今年摊位可谓非常吸引眼球，SEGA 摊位在开场阶段，也为广大玩家准备了钢管舞表演，吸引了众多人围观。更有美艳的《人中之龙》夜总会小姐轮流上场，令到现场试玩新作的队伍需要排队超过个半小时，要排到 100 分钟之后。同时间为《人中之龙》主题的夜总会女孩拍照的游客更加是络绎不绝。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1194841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="527" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 395px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而 SEGA 更加与去年一样，包下了银座一间 PUB ，举办了会后派对采用邀请制，主要入场包括贵宾、合作伙伴、媒体。现场除了商务合作对象外，更加多是日、韩的 KOL，设有享用饮品与食物招牌各位，亦邀请到了 DJ 演出 SEGA 旗下的各款游戏音乐。派对重点就是几位入选<span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">《人中之龙 7 外传》选拔的公关小姐</span>，分别是知名日本实况主 Kson、公关小姐「<span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">あゆ」、写真女星「</span><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">要あい」、AV 女优「佐山爱」、以及演员「中山こころ」，五位佳丽也盛装出席，共同为 SEGA 宣传。</span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
