            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>电子收费系统「八达通」免费推出全新钛金属系列手机卡面，以配合 iPhone 15 Pro 和 Apple Watch Ultra 的推出。</p><p>八达通发公告指，为配合 iPhone 15 系列于香港开售，今日（22 日）推出四款钛金属系列手机卡面给予 iPhone 和 Apple Watch 用家免费下载。该卡面分别为「极秘．黑」、「极净．白」、「极创．蓝」、「极野．原」。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-694x439.png" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-694x439.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-768x486.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-3-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-4.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-694x438.png" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-694x438.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-768x485.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-1-2.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-694x439.png" alt="" width="694" height="439" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-694x439.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-1280x809.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-768x486.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1-1536x971.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/1-2-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194786 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-22-13.54.21-387x580.png" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-22-13.54.21-387x580.png 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/萤幕截图-2023-09-22-13.54.21.png 488w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" />（图片来源：八达通手机 App）</p><p>不过，手机卡面亦适用于所有支援八达通的 iPhone 或 Apple Watch 新旧型号，不只限于新产品，只要打开八达通 App 内的卡面商店，下载「钛」Pro 系列个性卡面即可。</p><p>当用家将八达通转移到 iPhone 15 系列手机时，iOS 17 系统会帮助用家在设定「银包」app 时，列出所有的已加载的卡，以方便用家转移到新 iPhone。如在第一次设定时未能成功，只需要开启「银包」app，点击右上角的「+」符号，选择「之前的卡」，找「八达通」就可重新转移。</p><p>另外，由即日起至 2023 年 10 月 31 日，新客户加八达通入 iPhone 或 Apple Watch，再作一次消费交易，并于八达通网站登记优惠，合资格的客户将于符合推广要求的 7 天后收到八达通 App 通知领取迎新奖赏，在 11 月 10 日或之前就可到八达通 App 内的八达通卡面商店领取 $150 迎新奖赏及 1 张自选卡面。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.octopuscards.com/onlineform/promotion/general/registration/tc/step1.jsp?promotionRegRefCode=202309APO">octopuscards</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty